\id 2TI 2TU - Bible Iyansi
\h 2 TUMÀTƐ
\toc1 Un'kaan wàyweel akà Tumàtɛ
\toc2 2 Tumàtɛ
\toc3 2Tm
\mt2 Un'kaan wàywɛɛl akà
\mt1 Tumàtɛ
\imt1 Nsɛmà
\ip Un'kaan wàyweel akà Tumàtɛ Pɔl sye kàsön, ungö a un'kaan wàtàtwɛb akà Tumàtɛ anà un'kaan akà Titɔ, kisii a mbul 66 ungö a Yɛsu Klistɔ, u Masɛdwan a Filipe.
\ip Pɔl wa kàsön ntɔn mupà nswɛɛŋ akà amfum a Ikööŋ, muswaŋ naa andweer a baar, akaar, ambɛy anà asyääl bàkal aben. Nde kàkwen mufàbwey a Tumàtɛ ntɔn nde kàmɛn naa nkweel ande yà tsütsü, kyakin kàkwen nde naa Tumàtɛ usàwal nswɛɛŋ a ntsüü ntɔn Ikööŋ kusà a an'lɔɔŋ a loor.
\ip Pɔl kàkwen mukwɛy baar unsà làkwikilà utaaŋ a nkwaaŋ. Nde akaswaŋà sye ukwen muman Tumatɛ, ntɔn nde kàbulà u mpay: baar banswà bàkäl anà nde bàkyer un'tiin. Nde kàkwen mbɔɔn musyen Malakɔ, ntɔn nde kun'bay unsà isal ande.
\ip Unsà un'lwaaŋ ndaa ayuboo a un'kaan awà ayi: - 1.1-5: Mbɔr anà nsyääŋà - 1.6-2.13: Un'kanà anà lää - 2.14-4.5: An'lɔɔŋ a loor - 4.6-18: Pɔl anà Tumàtɛ.
\c 1
\s1 Mbɔr
\p 
\v 1 Mɛ Pɔl, ntööm a Klistɔ Yɛsu unsà ukwen a Nzam, asànaa ilää a mɔ̈ö akyà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\p 
\v 2 Akà Tumàtɛ, mwan amɛ wànkween: wɛy Taa Nzam anà Mwol abi Klistɔ Yɛsu bapɛ kab a ngway, mpem a ngyɛb anà duu.
\s1 An'tɔɔn anà ndɛɛl ntɔn lää
\p 
\v 3 Mɛ an'fuur an'tɔɔn mbɔɔn akà Nzam, awà in'fàsyääl mɛ unsà an'kyän anàbwaŋ, asànaa bàfun'syäälà ankaa amɛ. Taaŋ lanswà, mpib anà mwäänà, mɛ in'fatà din u ngyamàkà amɛ.
\v 4 Mɛ insàyɔbà nsaaŋ angye, mɛ in'fàkal anà ngyal akaman mbɔɔn, ntɔn mɛ in'käl aŋàyɔl a un'sak.
\v 5 Mɛ in'fàyɔbà sye làkwikilà a ndandaa awà ngye alà, làkwikilà làtwab atàkal a nkaaŋà wun'kaar Lɔwis anà ngwa Önis. Mɛ an'sà kam naa la là amu ngye sye.
\v 6 Lalan mɛ amàfayɔɔb naa: fɛl mbaa a kab a Nzam awà ngye alà sɛmà mpal kasi mɛ an'kɔɔ.
\v 7 Ntɔn Dweelà kan'pɛ Nzam kà là làbɔɔmà anki, wɛɛ Dweelà a ngwal, là ukwen anà là nkääŋ a mpem.
\p 
\v 8 Twon an'man nswɛn mutà imbäl a Mwol abi, twon an'man sye nswɛn ntɔn mɛ, mbuur a bɔlokà ntɔn nde. Wɛɛ ngye, man mpay mbwo mwɛy anà mɛ ntɔn Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ, unsà ngwal a Nzam,
\v 9 awà kitsü mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà kibel mukal un'sɛŋ ande, kà ntɔn isal abi anki, wɛɛ ntɔn mböön ande ŋàkwo anà kab a ngway ande, kab a ngway bipɛ amu Klistɔ Yɛsu kusà a an'taaŋ a mbul a in'tye.
\v 10 Kab a ngway alà lan'yàmɛnà apanà u mbwo a ngyeel a Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi Klistɔ, awà kàdwä ikɔ̈b a ukwà anà kàmɛɛy mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye u mbwo a Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ.
\p 
\v 11 Ntɔn Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ alà ban'si ba un'kyeey, ntööm anà un'lɔɔŋ.
\v 12 Lalan an'fuur mɛ a mpay ayi. Wɛɛ mɛ nswɛn a ya yatɛy, ntɔn mɛ in'kyàyöb naa làkwikilà amɛ là amu nà, làkyän amɛ là naa nde we anà ikɔ̈b mukaar indiir kan'pɛ nde tii Ilä kya.
\p 
\v 13 Lab mbaan a ndaa in'kyɛɛl ayi kàwem ngye akà mɛ unsà làkwikilà anà ukwen abà unsà Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 14 Kaar an'lɔɔŋ manswà amà bapɛ, u mbwo a Dweelà In'kyɛɛl awà amu bi.
\p 
\v 15 Ngye akyàyɔ̈b naa baar a Azi banswà bàkyan'tiin, asànaa Fizyɛl anà Ɛrmɔzyɛl.
\v 16 Wɛy Mwol utɔ̈l ngyɛb ande mbɔɔn udu a ndwà a Ɔnɛsifɔr, ntɔn nde kan'lɛɛl mbalà mbɔɔn, kàsàman anki nswɛn a in'siŋ amɛ.
\v 17 Wɛɛ, pa kàtöl nde Lɔmà, nde kan'leŋ làgyägyä, waa kan'mɛn.
\v 18 Wɛy Mwol kun'pɛ mbwo muman ubwaŋ apà Mwol kà ilä kya. Mbuur asin watɛy ayöb ubwaŋàbwaŋ asànaa ngye ŋakwo indiir kan'kyeer nde u Ԑfɛsɔ.
\c 2
\s1 Ŋità aŋàbwaŋ a Klistɔ Yɛsu
\p 
\v 1 Abun, ngye, mwan baal amɛ, wal ngwal angye u kab a ngway alà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 2 Ndaa kàwem ngye akà mɛ u mii a ambäl mbɔɔn, lɔŋ ya akà baar a lää ban'kwo mulɔŋ ya sye akà baar asin.
\p 
\v 3 Wal kab a mpay làngye asànaa ŋità aŋàbwaŋ a Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 4 Akà ŋità mwɛy tɛy afàköŋà indiir a mɛɛn mà isàkal naa nde akwen mupà un'sak akà mbuur kun'biil kà isal.
\v 5 Abun sye unsà an'taam a unüün, akà ŋan'taam mwɛy uwal anki ndä isàkal naa nde uläb anki in'kɔɔn a unüün.
\v 6 Kab a isaa atàtwɛb làtàkyà akà un'lem.
\v 7 Yöb ndaa an'tɛn mɛ: Mwol ayapà un'yɛnà unsà indiir byanswà.
\p 
\v 8 Un'yɔbà Yɛsu Klistɔ awà kàwiyà uboo a akü, awà mbuur a itoo a David, mulab Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ amɛ
\v 9 alà in'kamanà mɛ mpay tii mukambääm in'siŋ asànaa un'dwää. Wɛɛ Ndaa a Nzam kà yàŋàbääm anki!
\v 10 Lalan an'kääŋ mɛ mpem aya yanswà ntɔn bàŋàsɔɔl, ba sye bàwɛl mɔ̈ɔ̈, awà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu, anà làkoo a mbul a in'tye.
\v 11 Ndaa a ndandaa ban'kwo musà làkwikilà ayi:
\q1 « Kya bi isàkwà anà nde, bi isàkal sye anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà nde.
\q1 
\v 12 Kya bi isàman mpay anà nde, bi isàyaal anà nde.
\q1 Kya bi isun'tɔn, nde sye akyɛr asitɔn.
\q1 
\v 13 Kya bi isàkɔɔn akal bàlää akà nde, nde wà wàlää taaŋ lanswà, ntɔn nde ukwe anki mutɔn nde ŋakwo. »
\s1 Un'syääl aŋàkyey
\p 
\v 14 Yɔbà indiir abi, kyey u mii a Nzam naa yà ubwaŋ muwɛy an'sye ntɔn ngɔk ikɔ̈ɔ̈n ndöŋ, naa tɛy ma idwa mɔ̈ɔ̈ a baar bàweemà ma.
\v 15 Sà ngwal ngye ŋàkwo mumɛnà u mii a Nzam asànaa mbuur aŋàtsim, un'syääl mpa awe anà nswɛn, awà afàlɔŋ aswalaa Ndaa a ndandaa.
\v 16 Twon an'bilà unsà an'yääm ikɔ̈ɔ̈n ndöŋ anà mpa màfàlab làkwikilà. Baar bàfàbilà afwee amu ma, bàfàkàtsü unsà imbuur.
\v 17 Ndaa aba yà asànaa inkyär aŋàfüünà ifàdyà in'twaŋ. Imɛnɛ anà Filɛtɔs bà abun.
\v 18 Ba bàkyàwɛy ndandaa, bàmudwa làkwikilà a baar mutɛn naa ngwiiyà yàkyàyà itaan.
\v 19 Itàkal abun, an'sin a ngwal kàsi Nzam màŋàtsim, màŋàsà inyɛm a ndaa yi: « Mwol akyàyöb bànde » anà sye: « Wɛy mbuur wanswà afàtà ikɔb a Mwol din, utön an'kyän an'be. »
\p 
\v 20 Uboo a ndwà a kölàköl, kà nà indiir a wɔl anà arza mpɛl byàfàkal, wɛɛ byàfàkal sye anà byà in'te anà byà tɔm. Byàtàtwɛb ntɔn ibyääl, byumwɛy ntɔn nsyääl a bunàbun.
\v 21 Abun, isàkal naa mbuur mwɛy kan'pɔ̈ŋ nde ŋakwo mukaabà anà indiir abi, nde asàkal undiir mwɛy ntɔn ibyääl, wà in'kyɛɛl, wàndöŋ akà Un'lɔɔŋ, wàŋàkwo ntɔn isal aŋàbwaŋ.
\p 
\v 22 Tiin ilään a ndür a itö, waa aleŋ bàlàbal, làkwikilà, ukwen, duu anà baar abà bàfàbel Mwol u mpem.
\v 23 Wɛɛ, ntɔn mbaaŋ ikɔ̈ɔ̈n ndöŋ anà yà upool, yöb naa ya ifàbɔr ngwiy.
\v 24 Kyekà, un'syääl a Mwol ukwe anki munwan, wɛɛ nde akal mbuur bàkwen baar banswà, mbuur ayɔ̈b mulɔŋ, anà mukaŋ mpem.
\v 25 Wɛy nde ulwɛŋ asyeel a mbaaŋ unsà duu: taaŋ lumwɛy Nzam ayapà mbwo musɔɔmà anà muyɔ̈b ndandaa,
\v 26 muyàfurà unsà an'kyän aŋàbwaŋ, mutoo kà an'tɛy a ileŋ awà kakäär unsà isɔ ntɔn mulab ukwen ande.
\c 3
\s1 Ilä a ntsüü
\p 
\v 1 Yöb naa kà ilä a ntsüü isàkal anà an'taaŋ a mpay.
\v 2 Ntɔn baar bàsàbulà aŋunguur, asam a ngim, aŋangaal anà aŋuyɔl, bàsatoo Nzam, aŋun'tswe ngwal akà aböör aba, baar mpa bàfàfuur an'tɔɔn, mpa abye anà inzaam,
\v 3 aŋakɔɔrà, bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n ngyɛb, aŋankaabà, bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n nkääŋ a mpem, aŋankyɛl, ayiiŋ a yàŋàbwaŋ,
\v 4 ayääl a baar, aŋakii, ikwàmii ntɔn uyɔl, asam a ilään a ndür, akwànaa asam a Nzam,
\v 5 inzaam aba isàkal kyà nsà mpɛl, wɛɛ ba bàsàtɔn un'kanà a kya. Apɛ ngö baar aban.
\v 6 Amwɛy uboo a ba bàfàbilà u ndwà a ndwà, waa bàfàkur akaar a mpem a bɔɔl bɔɔl, bàŋàyɔl a man'be, bàŋàkwɛlà unsà an'tɛy a ilään a ndür byà ifà ifà,
\v 7 ba bàmulɔŋàkà taaŋ lanswà, wɛɛ ba bàfàkwo anki akà ikikye muyɔ̈b ndandaa.
\v 8 Asànàa Yanɛs anà Yambrɛs bàmbäär ba Mɔsɛ, abun sye baar aban bàfàmbäär ba ndandaa, ntɔɔb aba yàŋàkalà, làkwikilà aba ngwal latɛy.
\v 9 Wɛɛ ba bàsàkyà anki kwɛl, ntɔn unsil aba bàsàmɛnà akà baar banswà asànaa bàmɛnà unsil bàkäl akà baar abà bàbɔ̈ɔ̈l.
\s1 Nswɛɛŋ a ntsüü
\p 
\v 10 Wɛɛ akà ngye, ngye kàläb pànsi pànsi an'lɔɔŋ amɛ, nkääl amɛ, ntwaan amɛ, làkwikilà amɛ, nkääŋ a mpem amɛ, ukwen amɛ, muküünà amɛ,
\v 11 nkwaaŋ amɛ, mpay yan'yeel u Antyɔsha, u Ikɔn, anà u Listre. Nkwaaŋ nà mpa kàkäŋ mɛ mpem! Unsà ya yanswà, Mwol kan'tsü mɔ̈ɔ̈.
\v 12 Kyekà, baar bànswà bàfàkwen mukal unsà inzaam amu Klistɔ Yɛsu bàkyer asamɛɛy nkwaaŋ.
\v 13 Wɛɛ akà baar abɛ anà aŋaloor, ba bàsàlalà unsà ube taaŋ lanswà, mukur baar bumwɛy anà ba ŋàkwo bàkyer asakur.
\v 14 Wɛɛ ngye, tsim unsà indiir kàlɔŋàkà ngye anà kàkyey ngye naa bya byà ndandaa: ngye akyàyöb mbuur kalɔŋ bya.
\v 15 Ngye akyàyöb Ndaa Aŋàsɔn yà In'kyɛɛl sɛmà imbɛy angye: ya ye anà ikɔ̈b mukapà an'yeerà ifàtwaal ngwɛɛl a mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mbwo a làkwikilà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu.
\v 16 Un'kaan wanswà wàŋàsɔn u ngwal a Nzam we anà ndöŋ mulɔŋ, mutɔn, mulɔ̈ɔ̈n, muswaŋ mbwo a balàbal,
\v 17 ntɔn mbuur a Nzam ukäl wàŋàkwo anà ukäl anà indiir mukyer isal aŋàbwaŋ.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Mɛ amàlɔ̈ɔ̈m u mii a Nzam anà u mii a Klistɔ Yɛsu awà asàyà mutsul mbar a baar a mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà akü, kà ikɔb a mɛɛy ande anà kyà Imwol ande,
\v 2 kyään Ndaa unsà muküünà, itàkal utaaŋ aŋàbwaŋ, itàkal utaaŋ a làbe, tɔn, ŋan, lɛɛl, anà lɔŋ unsà nkääŋ a mpem yanswà.
\v 3 Ntɔn taaŋ mwɛy làkyer asàyà, alà mpa bàsàkwen baar amwɛy muwem an'lɔɔŋ a ndandaa, wɛɛ ba bàsàlab ilään a ndür aba ŋàkwo anà bàsawalà alɔɔŋ mbɔɔn abà bàsakyäänà ndaa ayà ikwen an'tsü aba muwem.
\v 4 Ba basàdübà an'tsü aba akà ndandaa, waa bàsàbulà ntsü akà nsim a bunàbun.
\v 5 Wɛɛ ngye, kaar duu unsà indiir byanswà, bäm mpem unsà mpay, kyer isal angye kyà un'paylàsaŋ, kyer ubwaŋàbwaŋ isal angye kyànswà.
\s1 Taaŋ amɛ làkyà lan'kwo
\p 
\v 6 Wɛɛ akà mɛ, mɛ bàkyan'kab itaan asànaa ibɔɔn, taaŋ amɛ làkyà lan'kwo.
\v 7 Mɛ kànwään ngwiy aŋàbwaŋ, mɛ kàmay ntiin amɛ, mɛ akyàkaar làkwikilà.
\v 8 Sɛmà apanà ndä a iböŋ amɛ yàmukandilà: ndä usan'pà Mwol, ntɛɛn a balàbal, Ilä kya, kà nà mɛ mpɛl anki, wɛɛ sye anà baar banswà bàsàkwen mɛɛy ande.
\s1 Nswɛɛŋ a ntsüü
\p 
\v 9 Sà ngwal muyan'man làgyägyä.
\v 10 Ntɔn Dɛmas kàkyan'tiin, kàkyàkwen ubwaŋ a mɛɛn aŋàbà. Nde kàkyen Tɛsalonikà. Kresɛns kàkyen Ngalàtyà, Titɔ kàkyen Dalmàtyà.
\v 11 Lukà mpɛl awà anà mɛ. Un'wɛl Malakɔ, yà anà nde, ntɔn nde wà ndöŋ mbɔɔn ntɔn isal.
\v 12 Mɛ kàtɔ̈m Tishik u Ɛfɛsɔ.
\v 13 Mpal ayàyà ngye, ntwääl kàzak a mpye kàsàwɛy mɛ u Tɔlàwas kà an'kɔɔ a Karpɔs, anà in'kaan, sin sin myà ibaan a ntsür.
\p 
\v 14 Wɛɛ, Alɛksandre, un'tsül a ngöl, kan'kyeer indiir ibe mbɔɔn. Mwol asun'fuur asànaa ayà nsyääl ande.
\v 15 Ngye sye kal kà igyɛɛŋ anà nde, ntɔn nde kàkyer atɔn a ngwal an'lɔɔŋ abi.
\p 
\v 16 Umpal kàsi mɛ un'lɔn amɛ wàtàtwɛb, akà mbuur mwɛy kan'bay anki, baar banswà bàkyer an'tɔn. Wɛy bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n alääb ya.
\v 17 Mɛ, mɛ Mwol kan'bay, waa kan'pɛ ngwal, ntɔn mukyään Ndaa ubwaŋàbwaŋ, waa baar mpa abà Ayuda banswà bàkyer awem ya. Nde kàn'tsü mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mun a ntaamà.
\v 18 Mwol asàkyer an'tswà mɔ̈ɔ̈ kusà a nkyeer ambe yanswà, waa usan'biil unsà ubwaŋ banswà uboo a Imwol ande kyà du. Wɛy làkoo làkäl anà nde u mbul a in'tye! Wöwöö!
\s1 Mbɔr a ntsüü
\p 
\v 19 Apɛ Piskil anà Akilas mbɔr, anà ndwà a Ɔnɛsfɔr sye.
\v 20 Elastɛ kàsàsaal u Kɔlintɔ. Mɛ Tɔlɔfim kàsun'wɛy u Milɛ anà ukyal.
\v 21 Sà ngwal muyà kusà a paŋà a mpye.
\p Öbulus, Pudɛns, Linüs, Kɔlɔdyà anà atɔŋ banswà bàmatööm mbɔr.
\p 
\v 22 Wɛy Mwol ukäl anà dweelà angye!
\p Wɛy kab angway a Nzam làkäl anà bɛ!
